      "cookedHtml": "<p>Exciting News! <img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/balloon.png?v=12\" title=\":balloon:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":balloon:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" /><img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/birthday.png?v=12\" title=\":birthday:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":birthday:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" /></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/confetti_ball.png?v=12\" title=\":confetti_ball:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":confetti_ball:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" /> We have created an automated birthday wishing system in our company for our employees. No more manual work for the company team in sending birthday wishes to employees. We have automated it through <a href=\"http://Make.com\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\">Make.com</a> and <a href=\"http://Monday.com\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\">Monday.com</a>. <img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/confetti_ball.png?v=12\" title=\":confetti_ball:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":confetti_ball:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" /></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/star2.png?v=12\" title=\":star2:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":star2:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" /> We’ll be sending out birthday wishes <img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/birthday.png?v=12\" title=\":birthday:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":birthday:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" /><img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/gift.png?v=12\" title=\":gift:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":gift:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" /> to our amazing team members on their special day! <img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/partying_face.png?v=12\" title=\":partying_face:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":partying_face:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" /><img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/email.png?v=12\" title=\":email:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":email:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" /></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/balloon.png?v=12\" title=\":balloon:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":balloon:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" /><img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/tada.png?v=12\" title=\":tada:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":tada:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" /> But wait, there’s more! <img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/tada.png?v=12\" title=\":tada:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":tada:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" /><img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/balloon.png?v=12\" title=\":balloon:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":balloon:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" /></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/calendar.png?v=12\" title=\":calendar:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":calendar:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" /> On Mondays, we’ll gather the list of employees who have birthdays and send out a special email to each birthday celebrant on their big day! <img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/love_letter.png?v=12\" title=\":love_letter:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":love_letter:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" /><img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/balloon.png?v=12\" title=\":balloon:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":balloon:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" /></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/dizzy.png?v=12\" title=\":dizzy:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":dizzy:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" /> Plus, we’ll also send a friendly reminder to all of our team members, letting them know that it’s someone’s special day! <img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/balloon.png?v=12\" title=\":balloon:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":balloon:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" /><img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/partying_face.png?v=12\" title=\":partying_face:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":partying_face:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" /></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/star2.png?v=12\" title=\":star2:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":star2:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" /> This small gesture is our way of spreading happiness and making sure every member of our team feels appreciated and celebrated! <img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/confetti_ball.png?v=12\" title=\":confetti_ball:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":confetti_ball:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" /><img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/partying_face.png?v=12\" title=\":partying_face:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":partying_face:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" /></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/tada.png?v=12\" title=\":tada:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":tada:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" /> Let’s make birthdays extra special! <img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/tada.png?v=12\" title=\":tada:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":tada:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" /><img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/sparkles.png?v=12\" title=\":sparkles:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":sparkles:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" /></p>\n<p><span class=\"hashtag-raw\">#Celebration</span> <span class=\"hashtag-raw\">#TeamSpirit</span> <span class=\"hashtag-raw\">#SpreadJoy</span> <span class=\"hashtag-raw\">#EmployeeAppreciation</span> <img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/balloon.png?v=12\" title=\":balloon:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":balloon:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" /><img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/birthday.png?v=12\" title=\":birthday:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":birthday:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" /></p>\n<p></p><div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/original/3X/c/4/c4c7463a9a83b24323310b93c8d7b7d772cab7f7.png\" title=\"image\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\"><img src=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/optimized/3X/c/4/c4c7463a9a83b24323310b93c8d7b7d772cab7f7_2_690x306.png\" alt=\"image\" width=\"690\" height=\"306\" /><div class=\"meta\"><span class=\"filename\">image</span><span class=\"informations\">1287×571 39 KB</span></div></a></div><p></p>\n<p><strong>If you need any implementation support kindly contact us</strong></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://calendly.com/msquarepro/meeting\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\">MSquare Support</a><br />\nVisit us <a href=\"https://www.msquare.pro/\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\">here</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCqidlIIwbejxZmRUWBICcjQ\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\">Youtube Channel</a></p>"
